reviewText: There are a lot of filler episodes before the Ninja Wars begins in this set, but overall it's good.  Can't wait for the next set.
Title: Naruto Shippuden Uncut Set 18

reviewText: My favorite episode from this DVD set will be the episode Revenge of the Shadow Clones or something like that. LOL. I just found the episode funny where Naruto was having a nightmare that his shadow clones had betrayed him, and they were causing all sorts of havoc. Maybe DVD set 19 will have some better episodes which it will be released on July 8, 2014.
summary: Not as epic as set 11, 13, 14 or 16 & 17 but...
Title: Naruto Shippuden Uncut Set 18

reviewText: I bought this box set because I have all of the previous box sets of the Series. This box set isn't as interesting as the previous two, most of the box set is about Naruto heading to the Land of Lightning by boat & all of the episodes are telling what happens to Naruto on his way to his destination. Some of the episodes aren't bad but they're still kind of weird, it reminds me of the old days with the original Series of Naruto.
Title: Naruto Shippuden Uncut Set 18

reviewText: The fight with Lord Pain has sent me love cataclizming to think everything can be on that level. This is not. But got to follow that path of Naruto to see his advancing so this must be in the collection.
